{"tid":124800,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人討論下二郎系既拉麵？","createTime":"2017-02-18T02:30:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T03:48:42.000Z","uid":16528,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7612926f367b8f846fc1d36cb004b508fc1ca415","tid":124800,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T02:30:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係大阪係過一次就返唔到轉頭<br />\n湯勁油 背脂多 偏咸 麵粗 量多 芽菜多 <br />\n唔同普通既拉麵鋪<br />\n去過兩間啲日本人連213244都唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲人只係負責煮麵<br />\n枱都要自己抺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/124dQ81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F124dQ81.jpg&h=79387de0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vSNvJSm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvSNvJSm.jpg&h=b53fb47a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/18/102433_f4af549276fda6408f6a6b5025446952.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F18%2F102433_f4af549276fda6408f6a6b5025446952.jpg&h=2aa90157&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔鍾意芽菜既唔洗試<br />\n細食既一定要叫細size<br />\n普通都300g左右<br />\n勁大碗<br />\n第一次食要男朋友幫我食左半碗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n差唔多間間都要排<br />\n架仔好撚鍾意食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/18/102434_433040ea2c543ee0ab6f29eab27ccc81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F18%2F102434_433040ea2c543ee0ab6f29eab27ccc81.jpg&h=1aabd5b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a7af7ddba9fcf772ce759c74a870b48e93cd29b","tid":124800,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T02:32:31.000Z","msg":"補麵圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T3Wkis1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT3Wkis1.jpg&h=47075009&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"936d71bff43886f0bd584fd147692a76c809ff66","tid":124800,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T02:32:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b02d80b54a908203099a913907f069b8b7ebb33","tid":124800,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T02:33:59.000Z","msg":"香港剩係食過混亂係呢種style<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要勁細碗<br />\n同普通拉麵一樣size<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5225c0d8041590bca333f8873c7642d3699833c7","tid":124800,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T02:37:59.000Z","msg":"原來得我咁重口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caa3f44df3a3d70a9705be04d5137b23eb7dad5f","tid":124800,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T02:39:23.000Z","msg":"喜多方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n四國麵王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你果隻唔識欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"447650503aecf611e257d0ebbf691c07f1355e84","tid":124800,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy